      <p>Bizarrely, I was hungry and had all of this stuff in my kitchen when I read this. (I hadn&#39;t bought a cucumber in months and months, but had half a cucumber sitting in the refrigerator.) It was delicious last-gasp-of-summer and I was delighted to have something to use some of my Banyuls vinegar on. More suggestions for &#8220;Banyuls vinegar, uses of&#8221; most welcome.</p>
    </div>

